    "created_at": "2016-10-31T18:28:57Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-10-31T18:28:57Z",
    "body": "I'm not sure why this stopped working in Chrome 52/Electron 1.3.0 and above but there are at least two different options to get it working again in your app:\n1. Add `file:` to your CSP policy\n2. Add `require('electron').webFrame.registerURLSchemeAsBypassingCSP('file')` to your preload  script.\n\nClosing this out since this does seem to be the expected behavior in Chrome for the current CSP you are using.\n"
  },
